Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.63,0:29:56.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everlasting youth?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.27,0:30:00.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I show you, Gen Hiraga?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.09,0:30:15.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.22,0:30:16.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:16.89,0:30:18.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:18.86,0:30:22.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NI'll show you nice and gently.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.40,0:30:24.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, I didn't come here to...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.56,0:30:27.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this everlasting youth about,\nanyway?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:27.93,0:30:29.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:29.14,0:30:31.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It really is golden.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.74,0:30:32.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.91,0:30:35.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You saw it.\NThere's something strange about me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.74,0:30:39.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The maid may be fooling you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.35,0:30:42.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a secret\nin the bloodline of the Hiraga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:42.85,0:30:45.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know anything\nabout alchemy?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:45.55,0:30:50.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's the mysterious science\nof making gold out of something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.32,0:30:52.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it can't be done.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.99,0:30:56.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But alchemy has contributed\ntwo things to humanity.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:56.46,0:30:59.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The first is the development\nof modern science.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.80,0:31:01.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The second is everlasting life.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.67,0:31:04.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One of your ancestors...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:05.01,0:31:08.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...became immortal through alchemy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.44,0:31:11.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're a descendant of that line.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.61,0:31:13.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding.\NWhat proof do you have?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:14.01,0:31:15.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, my mother...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:23.02,0:31:25.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My mother died.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.99,0:31:27.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.56,0:31:32.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that everyone\nin the Hiraga line is immortal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:32.43,0:31:35.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, up until\nthe third generation before you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.80,0:31:37.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...everyone seems to have died young.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.90,0:31:39.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That is, with one exception.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.87,0:31:42.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one exception being\nyour grandma, Sakura Hiraga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.28,0:31:46.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother lived\nlonger than most.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.41,0:31:49.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else died\nbefore they reached 30.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.52,0:31:53.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm not talking accidents\nor illnesses here, but rather...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:53.25,0:31:54.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...mysterious causes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.82,0:31:56.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did you actually...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.36,0:31:57.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...check all that out?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.86,0:31:59.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Jennifer Collins.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.09,0:32:03.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing graduate research\non the effects of aging.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.96,0:32:06.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to spring this on you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:06.87,0:32:09.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...but the mystery of\nthe Hiraga bloodline...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.44,0:32:11.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is the subject of my thesis.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:11.94,0:32:14.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My hypothesis is that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.37,0:32:17.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as a result of\none of your ancestors...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:17.91,0:32:23.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a significant genetic\neffect on the descendants.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.88,0:32:26.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because one of them\nbecame immortal...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:26.55,0:32:31.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm thinking that perhaps\nthe rest of the family...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.12,0:32:33.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...have been dying young.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:34.46,0:32:38.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But..\NIsn't that a bit farfetched?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.37,0:32:39.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:39.93,0:32:42.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,None of my professors\nwould believe in it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:42.97,0:32:46.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one thing\nthat can back up my thesis.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.14,0:32:49.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's your special condition.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.04,0:32:52.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want your sperm.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:53.51,0:32:56.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Aqua Permanence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.48,0:32:58.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:00.29,0:33:01.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please cooperate with me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:02.06,0:33:04.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of science...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.19,0:33:05.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and for my thesis.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.93,0:33:06.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.99,0:33:08.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:08.76,0:33:09.52,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.63,0:33:11.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:12.00,0:33:14.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:14.50,0:33:17.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At least it'll feel good for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.21,0:33:20.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.47,0:33:23.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.05,0:33:33.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:46.20,0:33:47.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.90,0:33:50.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A man like you can do better.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:50.94,0:33:54.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?!\NHow can I do it here?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.14,0:33:57.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:57.81,0:34:00.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you need some\nmental stimulation.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:00.38,0:34:02.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see if we can\nget you in the mood.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:02.75,0:34:06.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look. Like I said, that's not it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:08.39,0:34:11.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Impressive, aren't they?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.16,0:34:15.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still not satisfied?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.90,0:34:18.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll just have to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.00,0:34:25.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.07,0:34:29.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Special service for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:29.41,0:34:32.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This should get you going now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:35.58,0:34:38.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\NWhat's the matter with you, anyway?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:38.69,0:34:41.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look,\NI've been telling you all along.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.29,0:34:44.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now, will you please\ntake these things off?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:44.62,0:34:46.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How insulting...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:46.43,0:34:49.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is quite a challenge against...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:49.46,0:34:51.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my sexiness as a woman.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:52.97,0:34:53.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:02.28,0:35:06.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm just going to have to\nbite the bullet on this one.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.31,0:35:10.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\NAren't you ashamed?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.92,0:35:12.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:12.75,0:35:15.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it's all for my research.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.92,0:35:20.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, did your maid\nshow you everything too?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.13,0:35:23.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beth wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.53,0:35:25.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then, now's your chance!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.40,0:35:28.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you're not interested.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.14,0:35:35.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've come this far.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.68,0:35:38.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must help me with my research.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.35,0:35:40.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:41.35,0:35:43.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a guinea pig!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:50.92,0:35:52.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.50,0:35:59.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.87,0:36:04.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to cry about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:04.37,0:36:05.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're just too aggressive.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.21,0:36:16.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so down.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.45,0:36:19.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if you're not sexy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.09,0:36:23.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it just seems so unnatural.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:23.42,0:36:26.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to help.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.19,0:36:30.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are beautiful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.90,0:36:33.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If the purpose wasn't\nsome kind of research...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:33.80,0:36:35.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I could...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:37.40,0:36:39.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're so nice.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.92,0:36:56.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, no... This isn't...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:56.22,0:36:59.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!\NI got through!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:59.43,0:37:01.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I suppose...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:01.43,0:37:04.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried about\nwhat I was going to do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.16,0:37:06.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe\NI wasn't going to graduate.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:06.63,0:37:07.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.94,0:37:12.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue\nour research for humanity.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.31,0:37:13.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.11,0:37:17.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:39.33,0:37:41.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well. Good work.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:43.04,0:37:44.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.17,0:37:48.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is the Aqua Permanence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.31,0:37:49.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.68,0:37:51.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This'll help my research.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.91,0:37:54.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for\nputting you through so much.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.08,0:38:00.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that look.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.52,0:38:04.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll properly thank you\nwhen I complete my thesis.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.26,0:38:05.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:10.00,0:38:11.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.23,0:38:15.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's happened to your eye?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.44,0:38:18.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:21.64,0:38:23.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a minute...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.04,0:38:25.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.48,0:38:27.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I already have your sample.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.65,0:38:30.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.39,0:38:34.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.02,0:38:35.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.39,0:38:40.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:41.13,0:38:43.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's not like I don't like it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.70,0:38:52.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.66,0:39:13.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.82,0:39:40.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Mr. Hiraga here yet?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:41.22,0:39:44.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.\NI saw him at the gate this morning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:48.63,0:39:50.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:50.33,0:39:52.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the lecture.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:54.53,0:39:56.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Miss Ito?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.47,0:39:59.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.47,0:40:03.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen Hiraga was at the back\nof the college during first period...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.58,0:40:05.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...having sex with a blond!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.41,0:40:10.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:22.66,0:40:25.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me\nwhy you were late?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:25.80,0:40:28.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I here\nbecause you already know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:28.27,0:40:30.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody must have seen me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.24,0:40:35.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What I don't understand...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.48,0:40:38.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is why you would do\nsomething like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:38.54,0:40:40.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why myself.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:41.11,0:40:43.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know a lot of things...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.58,0:40:44.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...like about you either.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:45.08,0:40:46.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:46.32,0:40:49.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you worked\nat this college?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:49.49,0:40:51.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, anyway?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:53.26,0:40:58.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look exactly like\nthe woman in my dreams?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:58.26,0:40:59.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.37,0:41:04.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Does that have something to do\nwith what happened today?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:04.37,0:41:06.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.47,0:41:10.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But things have been\ngetting pretty crazy...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:10.44,0:41:12.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...since I first saw you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.75,0:41:15.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hiraga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:15.28,0:41:16.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.02,0:41:26.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here's today's report.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.93,0:41:30.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.96,0:41:33.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the worst.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.30,0:41:36.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:36.10,0:41:37.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ayumi...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.01,0:41:43.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder\nwhat's up with those two?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:44.54,0:41:46.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.55,0:41:48.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait a minute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.02,0:41:52.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you just go after any woman?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:53.19,0:41:55.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakurako has\nnothing to do with it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.76,0:41:58.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That foreigner in the car\nwas pretty, wasn't she?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.06,0:42:00.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did it feel good?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.59,0:42:02.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You get excited\nwhen other people watch?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:02.73,0:42:04.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a fetish of yours?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:04.96,0:42:06.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You scum!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.33,0:42:07.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.37,0:42:10.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Hang on a second!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.47,0:42:11.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know anything about this!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.97,0:42:14.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get your dirty hands off me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:16.04,0:42:17.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A bug?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:18.04,0:42:19.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.08,0:42:25.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that a strange foreigner's\nbeen messing with Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:25.52,0:42:27.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You think she did it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:27.62,0:42:29.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I believe so.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.86,0:42:33.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever her motives may be...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.16,0:42:36.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Gen is starting to ask questions.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:36.33,0:42:39.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,About the Hiraga bloodline.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:39.47,0:42:41.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And about Sakurako.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:43.14,0:42:48.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to tell Gen the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:49.18,0:42:51.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This won't be easy, but...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.48,0:42:57.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm going to ask you to\nbreak your vows.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.78,0:42:59.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go for me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.52,0:43:03.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for the sake of Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.07,0:43:23.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beth? Beth?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:24.88,0:43:25.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beth?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:44.10,0:43:46.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:47.43,0:43:48.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.40,0:43:51.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't approve of your interest.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:51.54,0:43:54.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Peeking into a woman's room like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:54.84,0:43:58.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Actually,\NI wanted to ask you something.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:00.28,0:44:02.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.08,0:44:07.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't really had a good chat yet.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:08.19,0:44:10.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my room.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:10.52,0:44:12.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have tea.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.63,0:44:25.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you don't know anything\nabout the Hiraga clan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:26.31,0:44:29.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Sakurako left the house...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:29.44,0:44:32.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...she didn't even send a note.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:37.05,0:44:38.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:38.45,0:44:40.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma, who's this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:40.59,0:44:43.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean the pictures?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:43.59,0:44:46.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Ms. Rokuhira's picture\nin our album?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:46.93,0:44:48.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's Sakurako.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:48.73,0:44:50.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, why is Ms. Sakurako...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:51.13,0:44:51.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.33,0:44:53.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this mother?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:53.83,0:44:57.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You say she looks like Ms. Rokuhira?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:58.07,0:45:01.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was surprised\nwhen I first saw her too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:02.44,0:45:04.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence that was.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:04.51,0:45:07.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And she even has the same name.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:07.75,0:45:09.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't realize...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:10.35,0:45:11.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She must've...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:11.98,0:45:14.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...been my mother.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:18.02,0:45:19.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, look...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:20.59,0:45:24.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Beth has been\nin the family for years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:43.18,0:45:46.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem\nany different than normal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.65,0:45:51.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have to look\ndeeper into its genetic makeup.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:51.16,0:45:54.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to use the university's\nequipment for this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:58.30,0:46:00.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? It's...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:00.37,0:46:02.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the home ofJennifer Collins?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.97,0:46:04.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to talk to you about.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:06.71,0:46:08.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.24,0:46:11.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have we even met?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.18,0:46:15.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.\NMy name is Beatrice Lambard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.02,0:46:19.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to make your acquaintance,\NMs. Collins.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:27.66,0:46:29.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:31.46,0:46:32.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:33.33,0:46:34.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:34.93,0:46:38.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it,\nyou're from Transylvania...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:42.44,0:46:44.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to me?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:45.58,0:46:47.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, I want to talk.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:48.25,0:46:50.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But, before that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:54.42,0:46:55.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! What...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:00.93,0:47:03.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really interested in women.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:04.40,0:47:05.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:06.13,0:47:09.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you probably aren't\ntoo fond of pain.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:16.88,0:47:18.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful body.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:29.39,0:47:32.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gen liked this body.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:42.40,0:47:45.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It only hurts at the beginning.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:45.57,0:47:47.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just relax.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:48.47,0:47:53.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to forget all about Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:53.51,0:47:55.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You will be my slave.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:57.55,0:47:59.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:59.12,0:48:01.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Madame.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:29.65,0:48:31.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Hiraga residence.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:32.28,0:48:32.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:33.32,0:48:34.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jennifer?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:34.75,0:48:38.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi. Something awkward's come up.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:38.96,0:48:40.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Can we meet right away?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:40.86,0:48:43.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And your grandmother too.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:44.53,0:48:45.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:45.60,0:48:46.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:47.07,0:48:50.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you tell her something dreadful's\nhappened to her maid...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:50.84,0:48:53.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm sure she'll know what I mean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:53.91,0:48:55.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With Beth?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:55.14,0:48:56.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:48:57.31,0:48:58.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:20.80,0:49:22.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:22.30,0:49:23.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beth!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:25.00,0:49:28.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Jennifer Collins?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:28.47,0:49:32.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my maid\ncausing you trouble.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:32.21,0:49:34.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. No trouble.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:34.95,0:49:37.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She showed up unannounced.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:37.35,0:49:39.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It took me by surprise, that's all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:39.79,0:49:41.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:41.19,0:49:45.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I hear you've been good\nto my grandson Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:45.59,0:49:47.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As the head of the Hiraga clan...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:47.93,0:49:51.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I offer my sincere thanks to you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:52.10,0:49:56.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like that mask of yours\nhides your soul as well.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:49:56.74,0:50:00.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Beth may not be\nthe most competent maid...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:00.54,0:50:05.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...as she seems to have\nmisled you somewhat.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:05.91,0:50:06.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:07.28,0:50:10.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking about having Ms. Collins...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:10.18,0:50:13.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...give some special lectures\nat the college.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:14.02,0:50:14.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:15.25,0:50:17.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In a backwater town like this...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:17.42,0:50:21.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...a native English speaker\nis very hard to come by.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:22.03,0:50:24.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And from what I've judged so far...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:24.70,0:50:27.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it seems yourJapanese is\nquite excellent.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:29.17,0:50:30.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:50.39,0:50:53.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling that,\ngiven your condition...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:53.79,0:50:58.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you might be experiencing\nsome type of discomfort.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:50:58.70,0:50:59.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:01.97,0:51:05.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you are willing to join us...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:05.87,0:51:10.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I can assure you that you\nwill be properly taken care of.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:10.24,0:51:14.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you will be satisfied.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:16.32,0:51:17.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:20.52,0:51:21.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:23.82,0:51:25.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone as weak as Beth...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:25.82,0:51:30.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...can live well\nas a maid in our household.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:30.80,0:51:33.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand what I mean?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:37.37,0:51:38.67,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:38.77,0:51:40.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What I require the most...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:40.94,0:51:45.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is the specialized knowledge\nyou have...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:45.14,0:51:49.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...from your studies\nat an American university.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:51.45,0:51:53.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am very interested...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:53.62,0:51:57.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...in the research you are doing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:51:58.32,0:52:00.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it's all right with you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:00.13,0:52:03.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I would like to be your patron.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:03.40,0:52:04.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:05.66,0:52:07.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:07.37,0:52:12.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think\nthis is a bad proposition for you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:12.87,0:52:17.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I think it would be wise\nif you'd decide quickly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:30.09,0:52:33.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen, will you carry Beth in?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:34.13,0:52:37.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will show Ms. Collins around.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:43.90,0:52:47.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd now like to know\nwhat you're really up to...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:47.14,0:52:48.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Ms. Hiraga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:48.97,0:52:53.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've been honest with you\nin everything I said.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:53.21,0:52:56.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My plan has gone wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:52:56.35,0:52:59.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, I thought I'd have you join us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:00.89,0:53:04.08,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You really want me to research\nthe Hiraga clan's condition?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:04.19,0:53:05.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For Gen.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:06.16,0:53:11.62,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one person I want to\nsave from the fate of our clan.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:11.73,0:53:14.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll give me free reign?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:14.83,0:53:17.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can provide me with a list...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:17.17,0:53:19.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...of everything you need\nfor your research.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:19.54,0:53:21.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrange it quickly.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:22.27,0:53:25.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, about my condition...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:25.48,0:53:29.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did not become\na puppet slave of Beth's.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:29.58,0:53:32.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There was too little interaction.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.28,0:53:34.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do not worry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:34.35,0:53:37.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your fear of sunlight\nis only a temporary condition...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:37.79,0:53:40.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and you will recover in time.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:44.26,0:53:47.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question I want to ask.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:47.50,0:53:50.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When Gen and I were...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:50.37,0:53:53.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...having sex in the afternoon...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:56.81,0:53:58.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...yes, well...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:59.14,0:54:01.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...he turned into\nsome kind of beast.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:01.55,0:54:06.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Does that have something to do\nwith his condition too?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:07.92,0:54:10.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A golden eye?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:11.82,0:54:16.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gen's condition is\nmuch worse than I thought.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:17.56,0:54:19.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:25.94,0:54:28.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great house!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:28.37,0:54:30.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've never bathed in an oak tub.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:30.91,0:54:31.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:32.04,0:54:34.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can really get used to this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:34.45,0:54:36.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!\NWhy are you here, anyway?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:38.45,0:54:41.21,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be living here.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:42.02,0:54:47.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As of today, I'm on the part-time staff\nat Hiraga College.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:49.13,0:54:50.75,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, you mean...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:50.96,0:54:54.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...you're taking on the research\nthat Grandma was talking about?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:57.04,0:54:59.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking this seriously?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:59.47,0:55:01.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all got to be a big joke.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:02.04,0:55:05.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to play with my cutie.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:05.51,0:55:06.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:06.61,0:55:08.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:08.35,0:55:10.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...don't you like me?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:11.38,0:55:13.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get it out of my mind.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:13.59,0:55:17.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That passionate sex I had with you\nin the afternoon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:17.69,0:55:20.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I've been looking so hard.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:20.56,0:55:22.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,For someone just like you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:22.79,0:55:23.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:23.96,0:55:25.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma and Beth are around.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:25.96,0:55:27.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:27.57,0:55:30.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Pay no attention to\nthe old lady and maid.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:30.30,0:55:31.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:33.67,0:55:37.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about not refusing a gift\nwhen you see one?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:37.14,0:55:39.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you know too much Japanese.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:39.54,0:55:40.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a foreigner?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:41.01,0:55:44.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I do not understand Japanese.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:45.48,0:55:49.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to have to\nre-energize this thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:53.79,0:55:55.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that. It's ticklish.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:55.69,0:55:58.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I said, stop that! Not there...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:59.97,0:56:04.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for putting you through that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:04.94,0:56:07.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:07.94,0:56:10.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As for Gen...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:11.08,0:56:14.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...I don't want him to\nsuffer the same things...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:15.05,0:56:18.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that Sakurako and the others did.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:23.28,0:57:25.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:34.36,0:57:35.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:38.13,0:57:40.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you messing with me\nlike that?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:45.60,0:57:46.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mother?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:47.47,0:57:48.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:49.04,0:57:50.87,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Sakurako.
